  "subject": "Make cnf-adapter instance creation more resilient to failure",
  "commit_message": "Make cnf-adapter instance creation more resilient to failure\n\n- check if instance already exists in createInstance such that\n  such a situation does not result in failure\n- this change is needed since retries of bmpn steps in the instance\n  creation workflow (that are caused by transient failures) are\n  currently not working due to the stateful nature of this service\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4272\nChange-Id: I3d7c8894cab09caa754bec3dd7c4e465f8ebe10c\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
